snippet.title: Amber Heard’s Texts Reveal Alleged Abuse By Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Never-before-seen text messages from Amber Heard to Johnny Depp’s assistant reveal alleged assault, however the assistant says the texts have been doctored.
